parameters:
I sense the presence of a strong opponent up
ahead... Should we proceed?

\nw[???]Hey there, I've been waiting for you. Thanks for
helping me out.

\nw[Taro]You seem quite relaxed. After putting me through
that...

\nw[???]Ah, you're the person from back then. It's been a
while, hasn't it?
\nw[???]Thank goodness, you have a really nice voice.

\nw[Shia]It doesn't matter if you have a nice voice or not!
Lift the curse right now!

\nw[???]I see. Shall I cast it on you again? It seems like
the effect is about to wear off.

\nw[Shia]What are you saying? I told you to lift it, so
don't go casting it again. Don't do unnecessary
things!

\nw[???]Well well, you don't have to hold back. Leave it
to me, leave it to me.

\nw[Saria]I'm not sure if we can communicate properly, but
can I assume that you're the one who created this
dungeon?

\nw[???]Yeah, that's right. Ah, of course I used magical
tools. I can't do something like that on my own!

\nw[Saria]Understood. In that case, I will restrain you.
Please behave and let yourself be captured.

\nw[Saria]It's because you caused a disturbance. There are
various things, but first I will conduct an
investigation.
\nw[???]I don't want to! I'm busy, you know!

\nw[Saria]It won't go that easily. Since you've done
something wrong, please reflect on it.

\nw[???]Why the hell! I was just waiting to thank you
because you helped me!

\nw[Taro]The conversation isn't making sense, and it seems
like we might not be able to communicate well.
Maybe it's better to catch you first and then hear
what you have to say.

\nw[Saria]...Understood. Will you come quietly? If you do, I
won't hurt you.

\nw[???]I'm busy, I don't have time to pay attention to
such things!

\nw[Taro]It doesn't seem like you'll come quietly... Oh
well, I have no choice but to restrain you.
\nw[???]Ugh, you idiot! I don't have time for that!
\nw[Saria]That is summoning magic. Something is coming!

\nw[Saria]I may have been too forceful with our demands. If
I had listened a little more, we might have been
able to negotiate something...

\nw[Saria]The dungeon might collapse! We need to escape
quickly!
マップ１３９にあるイベント２のセルフスイッチAをオンにする
